Classes
Class
Description
App
Main class of the project
endingCell
Sets up the ending portal for the player after the collection all the regular reward
endScreen
Displays an ending screen which changes based on whether the user wins or loses
Enemy
A moving enemy which tracks the player constantly
Entity
Abstract Entity class for any instances with initial position
gameMap
Sets up the map that will be displayed on the screen and used for collision
gameWindow
Instantiates and keeps the game functional
handleInput
HandleInput class implements the KeyListener interface for receiving keyboard events
mainWindow
Sets up and displays the window for the game
Moving
Abstract class which defines images for movement
Player
Sets up the player for the user to control and use to win the game
Punishment
Stores the position and the image for the punishments in the game
PunishmentList
Set up the punishments according to the game map
regularReward
Extends the abstract reward to create a regular reward for the player to interact with
reward
Base template for rewards which contain how much points players will recieve on collision
rewardManager
Places rewards and stores acquired reward points
specialReward
Holds everything needed to create and display a special reward
wallImage
Stores the image of the backdrop and if the object can be collided with
wallManager
The purpose of wallManager class is to take care of the location of barriers according to the game map, and the collision between the wall and the player
